{"tid":2193870,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好詩一首 ( 香港木蘭詩 )","createTime":"2020-09-08T07:11:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T07:34:21.000Z","uid":237465,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b186903f9fa32fdb42cc4c9472d2ac7190f676d9","tid":2193870,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T07:11:40.000Z","msg":"擊擊復擊擊，木蘭當港警。<br />\n不聞抗議聲，唯聞習主席。<br />\n問女何所思？問女何所憶？<br />\n女亦裝無知，女亦聽黨意。<br />\n旺角拖六甲，金鐘摔過肩，<br />\n元朗打破頭，太子抽長鞭。<br />\n同行二十年, 不知木蘭恨香港，<br />\n林鄭嘴撲朔，月蛾眼迷離，<br />\n成蟲傍地走，安能辨我有良知？<br />\n<br />\n來自   <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pckKprKHvuo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpckKprKHvuo&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqJMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=15edfa86\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pckKprKHvuo</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個頻道真係太撚正"},{"pid":"96dd5a03a045649ee75e033fed4fc61b4498ab6c","tid":2193870,"uid":367769,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T07:18:13.000Z","msg":"視網膜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea080f792470bfbd60a23cb4987204a6bd40e2d9","tid":2193870,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"96dd5a03a045649ee75e033fed4fc61b4498ab6c","tid":2193870,"uid":367769,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T07:18:13.000Z","msg":"視網膜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T07:45:37.000Z","msg":"什麼 視網膜 ?"},{"pid":"53733c2577a51d301f2838af948dd1a5d42031c3","tid":2193870,"uid":367769,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ea080f792470bfbd60a23cb4987204a6bd40e2d9","tid":2193870,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"96dd5a03a045649ee75e033fed4fc61b4498ab6c","tid":2193870,"uid":367769,"like":0,"dislike":1,"sc